<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;; font-size:xx-small; float:right; margin-left:-3em;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Modulation_techniques" title="Template:Modulation techniques"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a>&#160;•&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Modulation_techniques" title="Template talk:Modulation techniques"><span title="Discussion about this template" style="">d</span></a>&#160;•&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Modulation_techniques&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Modulation_techniques&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";">e</span></a></div>
<a href="/wiki/Frequency-hopping_spread_spectrum" title="Frequency-hopping spread spectrum">FHSS</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Direct-sequence_spread_spectrum" title="Direct-sequence spread spectrum">DSSS</a></td>
